# Project Structure & Organization

## Core Files
- [Pulse24Sync.jucer](mdc:Pulse24Sync.jucer) - Main JUCE project file
- [CMakeLists.txt](mdc:CMakeLists.txt) - CMake build configuration
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation

## Source Code
All source files go in the [Source/](mdc:Source/) directory:
- [PluginProcessor.cpp](mdc:Source/PluginProcessor.cpp) - Main plugin logic
- [PluginProcessor.h](mdc:Source/PluginProcessor.h) - Plugin processor header
- [PluginEditor.cpp](mdc:Source/PluginEditor.cpp) - UI implementation
- [PluginEditor.h](mdc:Source/PluginEditor.h) - UI header
- [PulseGenerator.cpp](mdc:Source/PulseGenerator.cpp) - Pulse generation logic
- [PulseGenerator.h](mdc:Source/PulseGenerator.h) - Pulse generator header

## Build Outputs
- `Builds/` - Generated build files (gitignored)
- `JuceLibraryCode/` - JUCE-generated code (gitignored)

## Documentation
- [BUILD_ISSUES.md](mdc:BUILD_ISSUES.md) - Build troubleshooting
- [BUILD_SERVICES.md](mdc:BUILD_SERVICES.md) - Build service documentation
- [WINDOWS_BUILD_GUIDE.md](mdc:WINDOWS_BUILD_GUIDE.md) - Windows-specific build instructions

## Scripts
- [build.sh](mdc:build.sh) - Main build script
- [build_macos.sh](mdc:build_macos.sh) - macOS-specific build
- [build_windows.bat](mdc:build_windows.bat) - Windows build script
- [cleanup-build.sh](mdc:cleanup-build.sh) - Build cleanup

## CI/CD
- [.github/workflows/release.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/release.yml) - Release automation

## Keep It Clean
- No build artifacts in version control
- No temporary files or IDE-specific files
- Organized documentation in root directory
- Clear separation between source, build, and documentation
